overview.en: Field Chain is an eco-platform for block-chain games. Players can use the trading platform for block-chain games. The trading volume and liquidity of virtual assets also have the right to circulate virtual assets at any time
overview.zh: 艾场是一个区块链游戏生态平台，玩家可以通过区块链游戏交易平台，虚拟资产的交易量、 流动性，亦具有随时流通虚拟资产的权利。
